s of the Past (album)|Ghosts of the Past]]''\n|-\n| [[Jebediah]]  \n| ''[[Kosciuszko (album)|Kosciuszko]]''\n|-\n| [[Papa Vs Pretty]]  \n| ''[[United in Isolation]]''\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\" align=\"center\" | '''[[2012 in music|2012]]'''<br><small>[[ARIA Music Awards of 2012|(26th)]]</small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\"\n| '''[[The Temper Trap]]'''\n| '''''[[The Temper Trap (album)|The Temper Trap]]'''''\n|-\n| [[Children Collide]]  \n| ''[[Monument (Children Collide album)|Monument]]''\n|-\n| [[Cold Chisel]]\n| ''[[No Plans]]''\n|-\n| [[Oh Mercy (band)|Oh Mercy]] \n| ''Deep Heat''\n|-\n| [[The Jezabels]]\n| ''[[Prisoner (The Jezabels album)|Prisoner]]''\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\" align=\"center\" | '''[[2013 in music|2013]]'''<br><small>[[ARIA Music Awards of 2013|(27th)]]</small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\"\n| '''[[Tame Impala]]'''\n| '''''[[Lonerism]]'''''\n|-\n| [[Birds of Tokyo]]\n| ''[[March Fires]]''\n|-\n| [[Boy & Bear]]\n| ''[[Harlequin Dream]]''\n|-\n| [[The Drones (Australian band)|The Drones]]\t\n| ''[[I See Seaweed]]''\n|-\n| [[The Rubens]]\n| ''[[The Rubens (album)|The Rubens]]''\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\" align=\"center\" | '''[[2014 in music|2014]]'''<br><small>[[ARIA Music Awards of 2014|(28th)]]</small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\"\n| '''[[Dan Sultan]]'''\n| '''''[[Blackbird (Dan Sultan album)|Blackbird]]'''''\n|-\n| [[Angus & Julia Stone]]\n| ''[[Angus & Julia Stone (album)|Angus & Julia Stone]]''\n|-\n| [[Ball Park Music]]\n| ''[[Puddinghead]]''\n|-\n| [[Jimmy Barnes]]\t\n| ''[[30:30 Hindsight]]''\n|-\n| [[Kingswood (band)|Kingswood]]\n| ''Microscopic Wars''\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\" align=\"center\" | '''[[2015 in music|2015]]'''<br><small>[[ARIA Music Awards of 2015|(29th)]]</small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\"\n| '''[[Tame Impala]]'''\n| '''''[[Currents (Tame Impala album)|Currents]]'''''\n|-\n| [[Courtney Barnett]]\n| ''[[Sometimes I Sit and Think, and Sometimes I Just Sit]]''\n|-\n| [[Dead Letter Circus]]\n| ''Aesthesis''\n|-\n| [[Gang of Youths]]